{
  "3088870": {
    "name": "千里山河录",
    "steam_appid": 3088870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款六边形拼图游戏，站在了同类型优秀作品巨人肩膀上的同时，也努力打造了一个拥有自己特色、能够为玩家游玩体验带来更多惊喜的作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/2af96f408080856593755eb725b367a4.avif?t=1763200402\" width=616 height=199 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过时光的缝隙，用着900年前古朴的画卷风格，玩家通过自由创造，徐徐展开一幅幅水墨丹青风格的壮丽山水人间长卷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/0236224626eb9df8a42a9c9e5c5ccc1b.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/173ce960fe0c2141ec2e3d0a3dc11fdb.avif?t=1763200402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras_big/173ce960fe0c2141ec2e3d0a3dc11fdb.avif?t=1763200402 width=800 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将与小千一同启程拜访中华美景与诗词古典，重新获得灵感再绘一幅当代的千里江山图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以全自由拼图玩法为核心，融入剧情冒险与Roguelike挑战，让玩家在休闲放松的同时再次遇见百年前的山水人间之美</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/dbbb1c5a01735c2d0b495ee10a76b821.avif?t=1763200402\" width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 自由拼接</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >区别于传统拼图游戏，在《千里江山拼拼乐》中块与块的拼接不会受到任何强制限制，玩家可以随意拼接，更多的自由让玩家能够进行更加非凡的创造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/2dc29a65ac8eedba5ac6dcd6398d6dac.poster.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/2dc29a65ac8eedba5ac6dcd6398d6dac.webm?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/2dc29a65ac8eedba5ac6dcd6398d6dac.mp4?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 景点探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果世间一成不变，那将失去多少韵味，所以我们准备了超多景点供玩家探寻，每个景点都拥有自己的故事、外观与特性，同时结合了一点点随机要素，为玩家从玩法上提供了更多变的策略性，想要更多的积分还是地块？又或者承担更多风险但是我全都要！一切由你决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/dd276111621adcaca2fbc75f16802ab3.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 景灵剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个景点都是凝聚了成百上千年灵气的角色，他们都有着各自的历史和故事，也有着各自的性格和特殊的能力。有了他们的帮忙，你的千里江山图将会更加的绚烂哦~~~不过，怎么才能把他们召唤出来呢，嘻嘻~~~~（^_^）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/599feb012e0552c07adbde252d1ef7d3.poster.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/599feb012e0552c07adbde252d1ef7d3.webm?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/599feb012e0552c07adbde252d1ef7d3.mp4?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/ea7f415b6857a8c43884f6c257afacd9.poster.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/ea7f415b6857a8c43884f6c257afacd9.webm?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/ea7f415b6857a8c43884f6c257afacd9.mp4?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/16393e9b10787dc0a6fceab35bcfe4ea.avif?t=1763200402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras_big/16393e9b10787dc0a6fceab35bcfe4ea.avif?t=1763200402 width=800 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在保持玩法休闲的同时，也想要为玩家制作更多让人突然“哇~”一下的惊喜！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > • 元素碰撞</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >山川巍峨、湖泽宽广、深山密林、阡陌交通、屋舍长桥、稻香千里···将山水画卷中的要素一一提取并总结，然后交由玩家进行自由组合：路到了湖泽便建起码头、来到了山川便筑成寺门···更多的碰撞火花待着你去探索迸发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/33046e7a1aebf3cbfaadd5d69da32c07.poster.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/33046e7a1aebf3cbfaadd5d69da32c07.webm?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/33046e7a1aebf3cbfaadd5d69da32c07.mp4?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 创造秘境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要瑞鹿游憩、仙鹤漫屋等等···为世间添加更多生机？在将常规元素地块按照特定形状进行组合时，将会产生秘境，为画面添加更多活力的同时，也能够收到丰富的奖励，不过秘境组合的发现可没那么简单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/5cb464e116a03d1ea18adf09403d4b98.poster.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/5cb464e116a03d1ea18adf09403d4b98.webm?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/5cb464e116a03d1ea18adf09403d4b98.mp4?t=1763200402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 还有猫？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款让人休闲放松的游戏，怎么会少了猫猫的缺席。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嘘~猫猫说要我保持它的神秘，那我就先不过多介绍了，最后悄悄说一句：注意了，有猫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/d45d14a69ea45c949ad4ce68667ed126.avif?t=1763200402\" width=700 height=394 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras/a15ccf5b0f832d9abdf97907cf2a2d14.avif?t=1763200402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088870/extras_big/a15ccf5b0f832d9abdf97907cf2a2d14.avif?t=1763200402 width=800 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还在开发中，更多的更多内容我们正在努力研发中，敬请期待 :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 有任何建议、想法或者期待，请和我们积极交流，一定会认真聆听（^_^）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >交流群：1002678966</p>",
